{"tid":799023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【打壓宗教】河南大規模強拆十字架 官方認可教會都要拆","createTime":"2018-08-29T17:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T18:27:23.000Z","uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4df0f1606aa669196eb538549a215467ff1907f4","tid":799023,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T17:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535503343_224d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535503343_224d.jpg&h=a7ec845f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n河南省多地近日發生強拆教堂十字架和衝擊教會事件。(互聯網)<br />\n內地清拆教堂十字架、打壓家庭教會停不了，河南省多地近日發生強拆教堂十字架和衝擊教會事件。<br />\n<br />\n據海外宗教人權組織對華援助協會等消息，河南省南陽市進入8月後，尤其近日多次發生大規模清拆十字架，許多教會遭官方人員騷擾，並被勒令不許聚會。而唐河基督教恩膏堂一位長老本月27日上午被捉走，目前下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n自今年5月以來，河南省商丘市寧陵縣開始要求官方認可的「三自教會」以及家庭教會的十字架，都要拆除。另外，包括洛陽、新蔡、安陽等地也發生強拆十字架事件。三自教會是指受中國政府認可（在政治方面領導）的「自治、自養、自傳」的中國基督教教會。<br />\n<br />\n據信徒統計，河南全省已經有100多家教會遭查抄、拆十字架、取締以及有人員被打傷。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音"},{"pid":"f2cee2b4e1d3c0c8aa6187f9f92befc0a4ec869f","tid":799023,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T17:28:12.000Z","msg":"唔知封唔封到聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f162c74bbe7f88a7288982540ef2f5325344282a","tid":799023,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T17:57:05.000Z","msg":"二大邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a664768bbaac3f8e393237fbdddeb696e74adadd","tid":799023,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n清末教案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06964f2d30a94b5545b8746ef39155d7053c5195","tid":799023,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"征支十字軍<br />\n幾時先會重組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n<br />\n八國聯軍來了人人爭住帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69465df12015bf30b55ef0e9a7040b961a2e3107","tid":799023,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T18:18:55.000Z","msg":"支那既將重蹈蜻朝覆轍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c417c370ff0b4d9f2631043d29bb3971c48b5a","tid":799023,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"依家天主教/基督教同一貫左膠一樣企係道理高地，欺善怕惡<br />\n睇下佢燒伊斯蘭嘢你啲支那人仲安唔安全？"}]}